      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ASH INTENTION (1) shapes well after a decent run last time, finishing second in a Special conditions H at Geelong in 22.41. Has the ability and looks a key chance again. ASTON PLUTO (2) was below best at her last couple, the latest finishing fifth at Warrnambool, but was among the placings at this track three back. Has the ability and can find best this time. SHE'S RELOADED (5) had the drop on the lead and went on to be beaten 2.25 lengths into third (22.67) at Geelong in a Grade 5 over 400m. The form out of her last race has been franked. Will give a great sight again. DRAGON TRAIN (7) missed the placings here most recently but can sneak into the finish with the right run.",
